  "title": "M&E Engineer/Coordinator",
  "description": "<p><u>Job Description</u></p>\n<p>Prepare M&amp;E works schedule based on the project master schedule</p>\n<p>Accountable for all M&amp;E works, site inspections, monitoring of progress of work &amp; variation order</p>\n<p>Responsible in ensuring that all M&amp;E works of the sub-contractors are in compliance to the Company’s and authorities’ requirements</p>\n<p>Review M&amp;E drawings and other materials submission prepare by the M&amp;E Coordinators to ensure that there are no discrepancies and/or conflicts with the architectural and structural elements</p>\n<p>To prepare report for the Consultant Progress and Technical Meetings</p>\n<p>To coordinate with clients, consultants, sub-contractors and project team to ensure smooth delivery of work including resolution of design and construction issues</p>\n<p><u>Education</u></p>\n<p>Relevant Degree recognised by PE Board or Degree Qualification acceptable by BCA</p>",
